{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"C\n      Hybrid — Instant on WiFi, Scheduled on Mobile Data\n    \n    \n      Mobile\n      Desktop\n    \n    Best of both: when on WiFi the app syncs instantly as photos arrive (like Google Photos). On mobile data it queues and syncs on schedule or when WiFi reconnects. Desktop app watches folders instantly. Manual upload always available with drag-and-drop on web.\n    \n      New photo\n      →\n      On WiFi?\n      →\n      Instant upload\n    \n    \n      \n      ↘\n      Mobile data\n      →\n      Queue offline\n      →\n      Upload on WiFi\n    \n    \n      Exact Google Photos behaviour\n      Most complex sync logic\n      Offline queue","choice":"c","id":null,"timestamp":1775816314814}
